      "title": "Bowserayaka diesel au. A young man of 25 years",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to the Police Media Spokesman's Office, 200 liters of petrol, 6400 liters of diesel and 25 liters of kerosene hidden in a garage of a house were seized during a raid carried out by the officers of the Kilinochchi Police Station in Karadibokka area of \u200b\u200bthe Kilinochchi Police Domain.",
        "This fuel stock was found hidden in 35 barrels. The arrested suspect is a 25-year-old Karadibokka resident. The suspect is scheduled to be produced in court tomorrow (04th)."
